Good morning, brother mine.

548
00:28:35,060 --> 00:28:37,390
夏洛克  华生医生
Sherlock. Dr Watson.

549
00:28:38,550 --> 00:28:40,250
您看上去  很不错  先生
You look...well, sir.

550
00:28:40,250 --> 00:28:42,850
真的吗  我觉得我看上去很巨大
Really? I rather thought I looked enormous.

551
00:28:43,120 --> 00:28:45,800
既然您提到了  这种程度的暴饮暴食
Well, now you mention it, this level of consumption

