578
00:29:46,630 --> 00:29:48,180
嫉妒杀人
Murderous jealousy.

579
00:29:48,180 --> 00:29:50,760
他给皇家天文学会写了一篇
He'd written a paper for the Royal Astronomical Society

580
00:29:50,760 --> 00:29:53,020
关于黄赤交角的论文
on the obliquity of the ecliptic,

581
