These enemies are everywhere...

596
00:30:26,740 --> 00:30:28,000
无人发现
undetected...

597
00:30:28,990 --> 00:30:30,730
无法阻止
and unstoppable.

598
00:30:30,910 --> 00:30:32,150
社会主义者吗
Socialists?

599
