1583
01:26:03,170 --> 01:26:04,130
会出现
there!

1584
01:26:06,930 --> 01:26:07,790
不
No,

1585
01:26:08,420 --> 01:26:09,820
别抵抗
don't try to fight it.

1586
01:26:10,040 --> 01:26:12,010
躺好  认输吧
Lie back and lose!

1587
01:26:17,840 --> 01:26:19,500
我们一起跳下去吧
Shall we go over together?

1588
01:26:20,350 --> 01:26:22,090
必须是我们一起  是吧
It has to be together, doesn't it?

1589
01:26:22,090 --> 01:26:24,960
到最后  永远是你
At the end it's always just you

1590
01:26:25,490 --> 01:26:26,870
和我
and me!

1591
01:26:33,070 --> 01:26:35,500
教授  麻烦你离我朋友远点
Professor, if you wouldn't mind stepping away from my friend,

1592
01:26:35,500 --> 01:26:39,680
我相信  他有点反感你的纠缠
I do believe he finds your attention a shade annoying.

1593
01:26:41,990 --> 01:26:43,810
这不公平  你们二对一
That's not fair, there's two of you!

1594
01:26:45,070 --> 01:26:47,490
我们总是两个人  你不看《斯特兰德月刊》吗
There's always two of us. Don't you read The Strand?

1595
01:26:49,590 --> 01:26:51,210
跪下  教授
On your knees, Professor.

1596
01:26:55,710 --> 01:26:58,620
手背到头后
Hands behind your head.

1597
01:26:59,350 --> 01:27:00,450
谢谢你  约翰
Thank you, John.

1598
01:27:02,750 --> 01:27:04,270
你什么时候开始叫我约翰了
Since when do you call me John?

1599
01:27:05,550 --> 01:27:06,970
你肯定想不到
You'd be surprised.

1600
01:27:07,210 --> 01:27:08,230
未必
No, I wouldn't.

1601
01:27:11,180 --> 01:27:12,730
你该醒来了  夏洛克
Time you woke up, Sherlock.

1602
01:27:14,910 --> 01:27:17,060
我是个讲故事的  我分得出自己是在故事里
I'm a story-teller, I know when I'm in one.

1603
01:27:17,520 --> 01:27:18,640
当然
Of course.

1604
01:27:19,450 --> 01:27:21,040
当然了  约翰
Of course you do, John.

1605
01:27:21,960 --> 01:27:23,080
他什么样
So what's he like?

1606
01:27:23,890 --> 01:27:26,310
另一个世界的我
The other me in the other place?

1607
01:27:27,330 --> 01:27:28,970
比看上去聪明
Smarter than he looks.

1608
01:27:29,230 --> 01:27:30,670
那一定很聪明了
Pretty damn smart, then.

1609
01:27:32,140 --> 01:27:33,540
很聪明
Pretty damn smart.

1610
01:27:33,630 --> 01:27:37,330
你俩直接私奔得了
Ugh, why don't you two just elope, for God's sake?!

1611
01:27:37,710 --> 01:27:38,980
无礼
Impertinent.

1612
01:27:39,800 --> 01:27:40,910
过分
Offensive.

1613
01:27:41,140 --> 01:27:43,700
其实  你介意吗
Actually, would you mind?

1614
01:27:43,990 --> 01:27:45,000
完全不
Not at all.

1615
01:27:55,130 --> 01:27:57,020
- 本来就该我了  - 是啊
- It was my turn. - Quite so.

1616
01:27:57,790 --> 01:27:59,880
你打算怎么醒过来
So how do you plan to wake up?

1617
01:28:03,330 --> 01:28:04,700
就这样吧
I should think like this.

1618
01:28:06,670 --> 01:28:07,590
你确定吗
Are you sure?

1619
01:28:08,580 --> 01:28:11,390
偷偷告诉你  约翰  坠落是杀不死我的
Between you and me, John, I always survive a fall.

1620
01:28:11,930 --> 01:28:12,780
可你是怎么做到
But how?

1621
01:28:14,760 --> 01:28:16,630
很简单的  亲爱的华生
Elementary, my dear Watson.

1622
01:28:50,100 --> 01:28:52,040
- 想我了吗  - 夏洛克  你没事吧
- Miss me? - Sherlock, are you all right?

1623
01:28:52,040 --> 01:28:53,820
当然没事  我怎么会有事呢
Yes. Of course I am, why wouldn't I be?

1624
01:28:53,820 --> 01:28:56,170
因为你可能刚服药过量  你该入院
Because you probably just OD'd. You should be in hospital.

1625
01:28:56,170 --> 01:28:57,390
没时间了
Hm, no time.

1626
01:28:58,120 --> 01:29:00,830
我得赶紧回贝克街  莫里亚蒂回来了
I have to go to Baker Street now, Moriarty's back.

1627
01:29:01,450 --> 01:29:03,190
我都希望他是真回来了
I almost hope he is,

1628
01:29:03,940 --> 01:29:05,510
如果能让你不再沉迷于此
if it'll save you from this.

1629
01:29:07,820 --> 01:29:09,160
现在用不着这个了
No need for that now,

1630
01:29:09,870 --> 01:29:10,910
我有真正好玩的了
I've got the real thing.

1631
01:29:10,910 --> 01:29:13,130
- 我有工作了  - 夏洛克
- I have work to do. - Sherlock...

1632
01:29:14,650 --> 01:29:15,670
答应我
..Promise me.

1633
01:29:17,900 --> 01:29:19,190
你还站这儿干什么
What are you still doing here?

1634
01:29:19,190 --> 01:29:21,170
你不是该去帮我搞个赦免还是什么的吗
Shouldn't you be off getting me a pardon or something,

1635
01:29:21,170 --> 01:29:22,750
像个好大哥那样
like a proper big brother?

1636
01:29:28,470 --> 01:29:29,550
华生医生
Dr Watson...

1637
01:29:34,200 --> 01:29:35,330
照顾好他
Look after him.

1638
01:29:37,220 --> 01:29:38,060
拜托
Please.

1639
01:29:56,850 --> 01:29:59,270
红胡子

1640
01:29:59,960 --> 01:30:01,540
夏洛克  等等  解释一下
Sherlock, hang on, explain.

1641
01:30:01,810 --> 01:30:03,080
莫里亚蒂还活着吗
Moriarty's alive, then?

1642
01:30:03,080 --> 01:30:05,410
我没说他活着  我说他回来了
I never said he was alive, I said he was back.

1643
01:30:05,500 --> 01:30:06,680
那么他死了吗
So he's dead?

1644
01:30:06,840 --> 01:30:07,530
他当然死了
Of course he's dead,

1645
01:30:07,530 --> 01:30:09,750
他开枪爆了自己的头  不可能活下来
he blew his own brains out, no-one survives that.

1646
01:30:10,300 --> 01:30:12,780
我刚刚为了证明这点而服药过量
I just went to the trouble of an overdose to prove it.

1647
01:30:13,930 --> 01:30:16,840
莫里亚蒂死了  毫无疑问
Moriarty is dead, no question.

1648
01:30:17,990 --> 01:30:22,160
但更重要的是  我很清楚他接下来要做什么
But more importantly, I know exactly what he's going to do next.

1649
01:30:32,780 --> 01:30:34,020
飞行机
Flying machines,

1650
01:30:34,020 --> 01:30:36,390
还有什么...电话
these, er, telephone contraptions?

1651
01:30:36,400 --> 01:30:38,440
这是什么疯狂的幻想啊
What sort of lunatic fantasy is that?

1652
01:30:38,440 --> 01:30:39,550
只是我对
It was simply my conjecture

1653
01:30:39,550 --> 01:30:41,100
未来世界
of what a future world might look like

1654
01:30:41,120 --> 01:30:43,640
和你我在其中角色的猜想
and how you and I might fit inside it.

1655
01:30:44,020 --> 01:30:46,140
一个逻辑学家应该可以从一滴水
From a drop of water a logician should be able to infer

1656
01:30:46,140 --> 01:30:48,740
推断出是大西洋还是尼亚加拉大瀑布
the possibility of an Atlantic or a Niagara.

1657
01:30:48,740 --> 01:30:50,180
或是莱辛巴赫瀑布
Or a Reichenbach?

1658
01:30:50,490 --> 01:30:53,150
- 你把这桩案子写完了吗  - 是的
- Have you written up your account of the case? - Yes.

1659
01:30:54,560 --> 01:30:55,690
经过修改把它写成了
Modified to put it down as

1660
01:30:55,690 --> 01:30:58,480
- 罕见的我未能破案的案例了吧  - 当然
- one of my rare failures, of course? - Of course.

1661
01:31:01,780 --> 01:31:03,240
《无形军队
The Adventure Of...

1662
01:31:03,740 --> 01:31:05,300
历险记》
The Invisible Army.

1663
01:31:07,100 --> 01:31:08,490
或者"愤怒军团"
The League Of Furies?

1664
01:31:09,550 --> 01:31:11,100
"恐怖军团"
The Monstrous Regiment?

1665
01:31:11,480 --> 01:31:15,010
我倒想起名为《恐怖新娘》
I rather thought The Abominable Bride.

1666
01:31:15,840 --> 01:31:17,350
- 有点庸俗  - 但会畅销的
- A trifle lurid. - It'll sell.

1667
01:31:17,350 --> 01:31:19,000
而且还包含了正式八经的谋杀
It's got proper murders in it too.

1668
01:31:19,000 --> 01:31:20,220
这方面你是专家嘛
You're the expert.

1669
01:31:20,230 --> 01:31:22,470
至于你的故事
As for your own tale,

1670
01:31:23,740 --> 01:31:27,420
你还确定你只用了7%的溶剂吗
are you sure it's still just a 7% solution that you take?

1671
01:31:27,420 --> 01:31:29,710
我觉得你是不是调高用量了
I think you may have increased the dosage.

1672
01:31:29,720 --> 01:31:31,700
或许我是有点异想天开了
Perhaps I was being a little fanciful.

1673
01:31:33,000 --> 01:31:35,690
但或许  这种事真的会发生
But perhaps such things could come to pass.

1674
01:31:37,050 --> 01:31:39,680
不管怎样  我相信我在那个世界会很自在的
In any case, I know I would be very much at home in such a world.

1675
01:31:39,680 --> 01:31:42,600
- 我看我不会的  - 我不敢苟同
- Huh, I don't think I would be. - I beg to differ.

1676
01:31:44,370 --> 01:31:46,990
但我一向知道自己是个先于时代之人
But then I've always known I was a man out of his time.
